divs: sighting detailsi was driving north on 121 towards the dallas tollway on the frontage road. i noticed a very large black\grey object moving east very quixote. no lights. i first thought it was a very large bird. i then thought it would have to be a prehistoric bird to be that large. there was no noise. i looked again and it was gone very quickly.
